9a2fe252c7b850dbadd1f","tid":1678374,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4RR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=65e67dc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4RR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=f10e81b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4RR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=6ea715a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"4520763d9042aada570e5483f33fbb8317fefb89","tid":1678374,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aeebd455d3a9d1345e8ab755c335858b39b28ad","tid":1678374,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1162f062bd97ee0daf66aee3cf76fe8d43306f2d","tid":1678374,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"太古已跪<br />\n冷處理<br />\n大家無拖無欠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"但太古持國泰股份唔過五成"},{"pid":"852893b39f2dbe3fe64dd6615e0f403359caa133","tid":1678374,"uid":18879,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:18:24.000Z","msg":"6月已經消費緊啦<br />\n<br />\n平啲嘅嘢：<br />\nMUJI<br />\nAMC 戲院<br />\n百佳 Taste<br />\n屈臣氏<br />\nGigasport<br />\nMike (因為LBJ 應該要抵制）"},{"pid":"54797c4b33c307ec54bf92bda0436aba4d06020c","tid":1678374,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18658a5f961ba79dc74ced6b539628158a85cf40","tid":1678374,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:32:47.000Z","msg":"好似有間中村藤吉<br />\n好過飲撐警美心Starb